    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Subject: FLYING DISKS REPORTEDLY SEEN",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "IN VICINITY OF SAVANNAH RIVER PLANT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "ATOMIC ENERGY COMMISSION",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "The Savannah Office of this Bureau has been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "informed that at approximately 10:45 pm, May 10, 1952,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "four employees of the DuPont Company employed in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "Savannah River Plant near Ellenton, South Carolina, saw",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "four disk shaped objects approaching \"the four hundred",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "area\" from the south which disappeared in a northerly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "direction. At approximately 11:05 pm on the same date",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "the above-mentioned employees saw two similar objects",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "approach from the south and disappear in a northerly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "direction. At approximately 11:10 p.m. a similar object",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "was seen by these employees approaching from the north-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "east and disappearing in a southeasterly direction. A",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "similar object was also sighted about 11:15 pm traveling",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "from south to north by the same employees.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "The disks were described by the above-mentioned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "employees as being approximately fifteen inches in diameter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "and yellow to gold in color. All of the objects were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "allegedly traveling at a high rate of speed and at a high",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "altitude without any noise. The disk shaped objects",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "referred to above which approached \"the four hundred area\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "from a northeasterly direction was reportedly traveling at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "such a low altitude it had to rise to pass over some tall",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "tanks which are in \"the four hundred area.\" The employees",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "referred to above advised the objects were weaving from left",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "to right but seemed to hold a general course. According to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "these persons because of the speed at which the objects were",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "traveling they were only visible for a few seconds.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
